-- Japan's Government Approves Central Bank's Plan to Buy ETFs, REIT Assets
-- B y   C h r i s   A n s t e y
-- 2010-10-28T12:22:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/japan-s-government-approves-central-bank-s-plan-to-buy-etfs-reit-assets.html
Japan’s Finance Ministry approved
the Bank of Japan’s plan to purchase exchange-traded funds and
real-estate investment trusts.  The central bank announced the approval in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Anstey in Tokyo at 
